# Backend Patterns Directory

This directory will contain the 10 production cache patterns moved from references/:

- pattern-00-connection.md - Deferring to request time with connection()
- pattern-01-cached-data.md - Basic cached data fetching
- pattern-02-server-actions.md - Server Actions for mutations
- pattern-03-streaming.md - Streaming with Suspense
- pattern-04-form-validation.md - Form validation with Zod
- pattern-05-optimistic-updates.md - Optimistic UI updates
- pattern-06-cache-keys.md - Cache key optimization
- pattern-07-cache-profiles.md - Production cache profiles
- pattern-08-cache-tags.md - Hierarchical cache tags
- pattern-09-extract-pass.md - "Extract and pass" pattern
- pattern-10-cache-nesting.md - Cache nesting rules

These patterns will be extracted from the existing SKILL.md and references/ files in Phase 2.
